        "description": "\"Cleric and Goblins\" is a thrilling VR action game featuring procedurally generated dungeons, a physics-based combat system, and intense loot collection. Your mission? To rescue the ever-unfortunate Cleric from a goblin-infested dungeon! But beware of the goblins' cunning traps at every turn. Battle your way through hordes of goblins, rescue the Cleric, and claim the ultimate loot in this hack-and-slash adventure!\n\n# Unique Physics-Based Combat System\nWeapons have weight and friction, and goblins are equally affected by physics. Swinging a sword lightly wonâ€™t suffice. **Strike slowly, Precise force, and Deeply Stab the vital points!**\n{845078274491310}\n\n# Rescue the Cleric!\n**Your mission is to rescue the kidnapped Cleric!** Navigate through goblin traps, save her, and safely escort her out of the dungeon! Remember, she is subject to physics too!\n{1043108787212519}\n\n# Infinite Dungeons! Aim for the Ultimate Loot!\n**The dungeon changes every time you dive!** Break through randomly generated dungeons and collect ultimate loots! Enjoy the adventure as many times as you want!\n{1979861309193631}",
